description: Sabyasachi Mukherjee is one of the most noted Indian designers. His collection includes elaborate anarkalis, sarees, suits and a mix of traditional and contemporary gowns. Notably, Sabyasachi’s wedding lehengas have given a new meaning to bridal wear by adding glamour to silhouettes of Indian culture.
